  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5593809/" class="title-link">【譯文商榷】阿克頓勳爵之箴言</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5593809"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bowen0607/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45211350-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bowen0607/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">東甌之蝦米</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-09-23"
      class="main-meta">2012-09-23 20:37:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5593809_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  阿克頓勳爵（Lord Acton）的箴言：“Power tends to corrupt, absolute power corrupt absolutely.”我記得在本書中被譯為：“權力導致腐敗，絕對權力導致絕對腐敗。”讀之朗朗上口，但細察之下，我個人以為這是一句誤譯。我沒有通讀過原文，只是單拿出此句，故而難免斷章取義...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5593809/#comments">(9回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 2没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            凤凰出版传媒集团，译林出版社2011版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5593809_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5593809_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





